        <p class="contact-intro">No pitch, no pressure. Twenty minutes to hear where you're at and share how I'd help. If I'm not the right fit, I'll say so — and point you at someone who is.</p>
        <div class="contact-meta">
          <div class="row"><div class="label">Email</div><div class="val"><a href="mailto:ish@collaboratec8.com">ish@collaboratec8.com</a></div></div>
          <div class="row"><div class="label">Phone</div><div class="val"><a href="tel:+447477522215">07477 522 215</a></div></div>
          <div class="row"><div class="label">Based</div><div class="val">Milton Keynes · Serving UK SMEs</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-form">
          <h3>Prefer to send a note first?</h3>
